bsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</u>.For example, <u>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</u>.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;As &nbsp;Seneca,an ancient Roman philosopher,once put it,<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;Almost any situation -----good or bad -----is affected by the attitude we bring to.&rdquo;Therefore,it is advisable to <u>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</u>.&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp;名言为古罗马哲学家西尼加所说：&ldquo;任何一种处境，无论好坏，都受到我们面对处境的态度的影响。&rdquo;</div>\n<div>\n\t在这里，名言警句可以根据具体所写内容所替换。所以，在准备的时候，多背几个名人的名言对我们写作是很有帮助的。</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p918645/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p918645\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914584/\">四级口语考试解题攻略（看图陈述篇）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914714/\">Quora 精选：如何才能更快地记住东西？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795419/\">有声双语美文：倾听与责任，是人生重要一课</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914516/\">宫崎骏老爷子宣布复出！新片圈钱已经不远了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914517/\">会背唐诗的川普外孙女 搞好中美关系大杀器?!</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914724/\">8个高效时间管理法</a></li><li style=\"margi